  "title": "Sales Engineer (Medical Device MNC/West) - Entry Level/up to $3700 #HAO",
  "description": "<p>Salary: up to $3700</p><p>Working Days & Hours: Mon-Fri Office Hours</p><p>Location: Jurong East</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>Prospect and generate new leads</p><p>Develop and maintain relationships with existing and potential customers</p><p>Regularly conduct seminars, product demonstrations and technical presentations to customers and prospects</p><p>Develop sales proposals and negotiate contracts</p><p>Meet or exceed monthly and annual sales targets</p><p>Meet or exceed weekly sales activities targets</p><p>Collaborate with the marketing team to develop and implement effective sales strategies</p><p>Monitor industry trends and provide feedback to the sales and marketing teams</p><p>Attend trade shows and industry events to network and generate leads</p><p>Job Requirements: Min Degree in Life Science/Pharmaceutical Engineering or similar </p><p>Interested candidates, please submit your resume to: allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>Ally Audrey Lok Xin Woon</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R21102307</p><p><a href=\"mailto:allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">allylok@recruitexpress.com.sg</a></p>",
